data.description: Beautiful Eagle River home only 1 mile from downtown shopping and restaurants, on a secluded cul-de-sac. Lots of upgrades to include new windows, new roof, flooring, a custom kitchen, stunning landscaping and much, much more. Sitting on nearly half an acre, this gem features $13k plus in professional landscaping, 3 decks with a deck weight-rated and wired for hot tub or spa, a fire pit, shed, and fenced front & back yards. Not to be out done by the exterior, the interior has new custom Anderson windows & sliding doors, updated lighting, a built-in custom live-edge wood entry bench, slate floors, and a wood-burning stove. Custom concrete counter tops provide plenty of space in a kitchen featuring a double oven, gas range, custom range hood, and hickory cabinets provide plenty of storage. The master bath features custom slate shower with triple shower heads and double sinks. Finally, don't forget the large 2-car garage with custom workbench, and RV parking. Assumable VA loan at 4%! This property is immaculate and not one to be missed.
